rture leads more efficiently, you need to rely on technology.\u00a0 Start with a basic self-selection tool or form on your website. Then, streamline your processes using automation and speed up your communications with TextExpander.\n\n\n\nTextExpander is the most popular knowledge activation software, with features that enable you to reach out to more prospects while keeping communication relevant and personal.",
